{"type": "article", "id": 61799, "title": "无畏女孩“搬”到了伦敦证交所，耐克破损球鞋受嘲笑 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-06T06:11:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 47871, "name": "无畏女孩"}, {"id": 7, "name": "艺术"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 1329, "name": "天猫"}, {"id": 5433, "name": "虾米音乐"}, {"id": 929, "name": "乐高"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190306123506EzwDCVvapbjcN4Rq.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"Q7hm\"><b>乐事连续四天公布了四位品牌大使，先后分别是<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4344992505551116?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">金晨</a>、<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4345356151722747?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">张佳宁</a> 、<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4345719793876665?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">宋祖儿</a>、<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/3562299047/4346084698534995\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">肖战</a>。</b>此外，江疏影和林更新为品牌代言人。尽管现在无代言不品牌，但我们依然不知道薯片代言人是一种怎样的需求。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123546PropFdkTqmC29tIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.541000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123546Xi0ujSBZ7FW8gIPU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.541000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903061235465uwL3Qbs1TmiylAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.541000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903061235476jKMU0ra5Pfe4hBZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.541000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"mBhu\"><b>妇女节之际，喜茶和太平鸟在春节礼盒之后再次跨界合作推出 T 恤，并设计了联名主题图案。</b>包括黑粉短款 T 恤、白黄长款 T 恤 。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123617ZbH7kyzBoLexFA1n.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665505\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903061236176tP5c3WFfQxuXNAH.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.326389\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123629hsZ0dK1rM3e4flgO.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.398148\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"mBhu\">此外，喜茶门店还将在 3 月 7 日——3 月 8 日推出玫瑰冰激凌，饮品上还带有“T 恤型杯套”。消费者购买两杯饮品会得到一张刮刮乐，可能会刮出限量帆布包。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123658Gmpewn8Nf2XHc7j3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497965\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123645T7w6mniKLtPGvoSq.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499171\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"NjXi\"><a href=\"https://www.skymark.co.jp/ja/campaign/bleague/?fbclid=IwAR0c9EVJ0xYYL7tYOHiE4ELTCGzGNWnM20QMIiHBAANgT890BLGPrvwdZr0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>最近，《灌篮高手》作者井上雄彥和日本篮球联盟 B.League 、日本天马航空（Skymark Airlines）合作，打造了 B.League JET 定制班机。</b></a>飞机外部涂装了《灌篮高手》的人物肖像，内部也采用了定制装饰，还设计了同风格的行李签。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123715gOxSG1uezdP9yjpf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.601111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123715W1Ntr3BLCeHh0XUo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123715e1cBY8anIMzQsbXv.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.169540\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123715XRcHUp4K29ruifOe.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.700000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"Ojwe\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTQxOTE5Njc0MQ==&amp;mid=2653892807&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8d5d21fdb0185646e781a4c6d8db1672&amp;chksm=67735eed5004d7fbe98a67903104e127cb125f9e4e2222cca7226e1dedbdd085efb72f0fb9f4&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0305AiaEfAKcEqv60fHztQUG&amp;key=f1b1b4aaf75e0cb58101ba8a73fdb78f676958b212aa723d1c85b647ca20656542f1a9e7c73013d20b0981ea3996c25635eaa8421b794ca956f4aee73bcb611ac0aa167a7d4f95d1b6dc5d48ccf557b6&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=Gv4HhK3N1i3Bo9dZ8zLb9M%2Bj8bhvIQxqCqBwE1GYAwRSvkwDyPeVoy89VLfgGSsi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天猫发布了妇女节主题广告片《女人该不该按标准活》，</b></a>分别和 40 岁、30 岁以及 20 岁的女性对话，表达不必按照年龄标准来限定自己的生活。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s08441c5irw\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"oajC\"><a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2019/03/05/a-fearless-girl-statue-comes-to-london.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“无畏女孩”在妇女节时候，来到了伦敦证券交易所门口。</b></a>不过这不是一直在纽约证券交易所门口的雕塑，实际上是 State Street Global Advisors（SSGA）推出的复制品， 预计将在伦敦待三个月。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123804ICnQkfR2scO9zVaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523560\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123804rA8VpZNoX0xm4yKk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123804wrK1fcPM0vQZmFaG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"2Lh8\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4346210535854459?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>虾米音乐和礼橙专车将在 UCCA 尤伦斯当代艺术中心启动“城籁”新媒体艺术展。</b></a>艺术家陈微和虾米音乐人李星宇联合创作馆内的视听呈现效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s0845vasswy\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123848E7m0WAjw9ipQlMhG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123848QJtwjGxUk7WTZnPi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.331481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306123848jfUVvLYhaAmS95Fu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"xwbT\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4346067246271923?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>京东电脑数码拍了支“巅峰 24 小时”的广告片。</b></a>片中“网速”被谋杀，侦探分别审问了嫌疑人手机、宽带、路由器和隔壁电脑，引出京东昨天高速路由器的促销活动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b08452712gt\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"6AJA\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BEA3xZmNoHA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>新西伯利亚 S7 航空一系列设想了外星人到访地球的广告片，</b></a>将地球拆分成 6 个主题讲述，分别是自然、食物、派对、艺术、体育和爱情。创意代理商是 W+K 阿姆斯特丹。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=q0845xbde8u\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k0845zxq2ty\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"Wd6a\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/LEGO_Group/status/1102539211834576902/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>乐高昨天在Twitter 上发布了一款叫做 “LEGO Fold” 的玩具，</b></a>和三星推出的折叠手机形状十分相似。其实这款产品 2018 年 11 月就面世了，借机调侃三星并来表达象力永远不会遇到电量耗尽的状况。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306124059c02CPmMsiA4Y1znb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"w7oP\">另外一支借势营销广告来自 Skechers。<b><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/zion-williamson-skechers-reactions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">它在《纽约时报》、《今日美国》等纸质媒体和 Instagram 等社交媒体发布了 “Just Blew It” 广告</a>，</b>来借机嘲讽 Nike 在NCCA 赛事上的爆鞋事件。</p><p line=\"w7oP\">广告图故意选了双和锡安脚下几乎一模一样的球鞋，大标题写着 “Just Blew It”（这回可搞砸了），下面小字写着 “We won’t split on you”（我们不会让你的球鞋裂开）。</p><p line=\"w7oP\" class=\"\">不过 Nike 的前设计师<st-div>&nbsp;Tiffany Beers 已经表示过这种事情很罕见。此外 Skechers 的篮球鞋还没优秀到出现在 NCCA 或者 NBA 的赛场上，广告更多是在博眼球。</st-div></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903061241420scSTNF56QYhXjg1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306124142A0LtI6NJQszWB197.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.125887\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306124227Dbp5Ro2K8CNkPxL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.164905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"w7oP\" class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2019/03/05/a-fearless-girl-statue-comes-to-london.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">CNBC</a></p>"}